WEBVTT

00:01.983 --> 00:03.467
My parents are in town.

00:03.469 --> 00:05.302
Would you please leave out
of the back door?

00:05.304 --> 00:07.071
Eric and I parted ways.

00:07.073 --> 00:08.172
Do you want me
to just stop working

00:08.173 --> 00:09.640
so I can chauffeur
the kids around?

00:09.642 --> 00:11.609
I think they should come
live with me full time.

00:11.611 --> 00:13.978
You look nice.

00:13.980 --> 00:15.846
I tend to be
a teeny bit sensitive

00:15.848 --> 00:19.116
when challenged about my
allegiance to my culture.

00:19.118 --> 00:21.886
I have to leave the country
for a couple days.

00:21.888 --> 00:22.920
But when I get back,

00:22.922 --> 00:24.321
I'd like to sit down
and talk about

00:24.323 --> 00:26.457
you and I seeing one another
and how that might look.

00:26.459 --> 00:29.001
Sounds like something
I might look forward to.

